summary: Heyyyyy, about what you said about Dans channel- I agree to an extent but I think he’s taking care of himself- not giving...
question: Heyyyyy, about what you said about Dans channel- I agree to an extent but I think he’s taking care of himself- not giving himself the emotional stress of having to film a video. Videos on the gaming channel don’t require much effort as they can just play a game, but Dan probably wants to put as much effort as possible into a video. I can see where your coming from though. (Please don’t hate me I’m shy) Yeet 💕
answer:
nah i understand where you are coming from with this. I know people are saying it’s because of his mental health which is of course okay in all circumstances, however i feel as if he’s kinda pushed away his channel and is dedicated to gaming and phil?

I think people need to stop pushing everything dan does too his depression. y’all are literally turning it into a thing where dan can be let off any scenario because of it. dan literally said himself that he doesn’t let it define him. i am not forcing him to produce a video but i just think, he can wholeheartedly create a video for his channel whilst on tour. if he can make videos with phil, then surely he can make videos for himself?

idk, people have been hating on me since i posted the thing about his channel, and people have been saying that no one thinks that and it’s up to him. of course it’s up to him, but come off it, i’ve seen everyone with their ‘where is dans june video?’ and ‘dans appeared on phils channel more than his own this year’ posts. don’t deny it to make yourself seem like some saint. you’re allowed to have an opinion.


didn’t y’all learn anything from dans channel?

title: DNP Oneshot (sad warning)
body:
I grab his wrist.

-Dan you don’t have to leave. I can help you. - I said quietly.

He slowly turned around and looked at me. His eyes were red and very sad. I could clearly see he was crying.

-But what’s the sense Phil? I have this fucking depression and I’m just unable to believe you love me. I just can’t and don’t want anyone to care about me because why would they? Why would you? - he asked.

-Because I do care about you. I want do, I do and I will. I love you, Dan. Maybe you won’t believe it but I do and nothing’s going to change that.

He sighed and nervously tightened his lips.

-Well then that’s only making things worse because I’m going to hurt you even more.

-Not if you will just stay. Just stay with me, Dan - I said started crying. 

I couldn’t lose him. He was my fan, my Internet friend, my best friend, my roommate, maybe even someone more. He was just my Dan…

Dan walked closer and let his head rest on my forehead. We were just staying in our hallway, sticking our foreheads and crying. Because we knew that’s the end. He won’t do youtube anymore so why would I? He’s not going to live with me anymore so I’m going to be alone because why would I even bother myself looking for replacement? He won’t live anymore and I can’t do anything because he won’t let me and he’s going to hate me if I will. And yeah, I promised him that I won’t do the same thing, that I’m going to live. 

He carefully stepped back and looked at me. I can assure you that whenever the person you love will give you this look…you just know. That he loves you too.

-Goodbye Phil - he whispered in my hair and left the hallway.

I was crying. I promised him won’t to the same thing, I’m going to live. But the truth is that in the moment he was leaving me, his home, his career, his entire life. I was already dead.

And only after an hour standing there and crying I had a strength to speak:

-Goodbye Dan…
